      <div id="offer" class="tab-pane fade show active">

        <p>No need to go to the country! - Here is a 6 month language learning bootcamp to develop fluency in Chinese that is done entirely from the comfort of your own home!</p>

        <p>Online exercises to complete before the zoom sessions (3 sessions per week).</p>

        <p>During the Zoom session, the teacher gives general feedback to the group based on exercise submissions (reading/recital/writing).</p>

        <p>Students go into breakout rooms for ‘structured production’ sessions, they can choose:
          <ul>
            <li>To do a presentation based on the writing text they produced during the online exercises;</li>
            <li>To do a presentation based on the existing reading text given for that day’s online exercises;</li>
            <li>To converse with their breakout room buddy in Chinese for practice purposes.</li>
          </ul>
        At the end of the session, TAs recommend/encourage groups/pairs/individuals to do their presentations/dialogues in front of the rest of the group to celebrate the fruits of their learning for the day and to obtain feedback.</p>

        <p>Benefits of the breakout room/buddy system:
          <ul>
            <li>Students can help each other learn;</li>
            <li>Students can practise Chinese conversation with each other;</li>
            <li>TAs can pop into the rooms to help with any questions;</li>
            <li>Students can create tickets to practise with a TA or to ask questions.</li>
          </ul>
        <p>

